org.js4ms.service.protocol.rest.message
Class ProtocolVersion

java.lang.Object
  org.js4ms.service.protocol.rest.message.ProtocolVersion

public final class ProtocolVersion
extends Object

A protocol version identifier. Provides methods for parsing and serializing a protocol version string that appears in request and response messages.

Author:
Gregory Bumgardner
